**What changed:**

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| Hardcoded `DB_PATH`, `LOG_FILE`, credentials | `os.getenv("LOG_FILE", ...)` / `os.getenv("DB_PATH", ...)` |
| String formatting in SQL (`%s`, `%d`) | Parameterized queries (`?` placeholders) |
| One monolithic `proc_data()` | `extract_logs` → `transform_errors` / `transform_api_stats` → `load_to_db` / `generate_report` |
| `line.split(" ")` parsing | `re.compile` with named groups (`LOG_RE`, `_USER_RE`, `_API_RE`) |
| No type hints, no docs | All functions typed + docstringed |

